    • send

      java.util.Optional<HsmsMessage> send​(HsmsMessage msg) throws HsmsSendMessageException, HsmsWaitReplyMessageException, HsmsException, java.lang.InterruptedException
      Send HSMS-Message and receive Reply-Message if exist.
      パラメータ:
      msg - the HSMS Message
      戻り値:
      Optional has value if Reply-Message exist
      例外:
      HsmsSendMessageException - if send message failed
      HsmsWaitReplyMessageException - if reply message timeout
      HsmsException - if HSMS communicate failed
      java.lang.InterruptedException - if interrupted
